@Pierrestro I didn't wonder how to install Windows 2000 and Windows XP in DOSBox-X, I already know how to do it, and that without starting the installation in a previous Windows.
What I was wondering was how to get RetroArch versions for from Windows 95 to Windows XP (there doesn't seem to be a RetroArch for Windows NT 4.0) to run on the mentioned operating systems.

